## Key findings
- FCN1 is only lectin complement gene expressed in PBMCs (monocytes ~5x); MBL2/MASP1/2 near-zero (liver-expressed)
- Pre-IVIG PANS innate/adaptive ratio = 3.88 vs controls = 4.23 (scRNA-seq) — supports innate deficiency hypothesis
- Post-IVIG ratio jumps to 7.92
- Innate cytokine flare effect (1.30) > adaptive (1.05); IL-10 regulatory downregulated
- Lectin complement pathway is #1 enriched (FDR=1.12e-5) in PANS variants

